.TE

.SH SEE ALSO
.sp
.LP
\fBsys-unconfig\fR(1M), \fBsysidtool\fR(1M), \fBattributes\fR(5)
.SH DIAGNOSTICS
.sp
.LP
When run without options, a log of the \fBsysidconfig\fR program's activity can be found in \fB/var/log/sysidconfig.log\fR. This file contains a timestamp log of each program executed, its resulting \fBstderr\fR output, and its exit code. If an application in the list was not found or is not executable, that will also be noted.
